{"TopicId":151775,"ForumId":18,"TopicTitle":"Happy Carl Sagan Day!!","CreatedByName":"Chiron0224","CreatedById":147812,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-09T16:58:51Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Chiron0224","CreatedById":147812,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-09T16:58:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022150611A-Sagan.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022600\u0022 src=\u0022https://media.boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/150611A-Sagan.jpg\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"monstah","CreatedById":95210,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-09T17:26:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAw, damn, why didn\u0027t I wear \u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.redbubble.com/people/phoarpia/works/23066501-sagan\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ethis\u003C/a\u003E to work today?? \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:(\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Aziz","CreatedById":150811,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-09T18:07:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI know that name, but have no clue who he is.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Firemetal","CreatedById":164725,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-09T18:20:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222844738\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022151775\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221478714859\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150811\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The Aziz\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n13 minutes ago, The Aziz said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI know that name, but have no clue who he is.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHe was a teacher who tought astrophysicics I think. He had a television show where he tought people about the cosmos.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFire\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-11-09T18:21:51Z\u0022 title=\u002211/09/2016 06:21  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003ENovember 9, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Firemetal\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EDang auto-correct!!!\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Chiron0224","CreatedById":147812,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-09T19:44:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHe was a major proponent of science and skepticism.\u00A0 His life mission was to bring science to the masses.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mikki","CreatedById":137508,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-09T20:40:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have a book from Mr. Sagan in my library, \u0022The Comet\u0022, a nice explanation of\u00A0chemistry\u00A0of the content in\u00A0the Oort cloud and other objects in our Solar system. Intriguing stuff.\u003Cbr\u003E\nFrom the early 80\u0060s, i got hooked in Childhood with such\u00A0lecture. I would like to build miningmachines and refinerys for other planets, but i guess i was born way to early\u00A0for such tasks\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:wink:\u0022\u003E.\u003Cbr\u003E\nGood man, Carl Sagan.\u00A0\u00A0\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MaxxQ","CreatedById":102622,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-09T21:00:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHe\u0027s also the author of Contact, that the movie was based on, and was Neil DeGrasse Tyson\u0027s mentor.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Starhawk","CreatedById":131400,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-09T21:28:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPerhaps most importantly he was the creator and host of Cosmos: A Personal Voyage.\u00A0 A most excellent series.\u00A0 I remember it very fondly.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHappy landings!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Chiron0224","CreatedById":147812,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-09T21:30:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ll be watching my Cosmos DVD box set and enjoying some of Carl\u0027s favorite recreational substance while doing so.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"moogoob","CreatedById":118251,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-09T23:51:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCan\u0027t forget that he was a founding member of the Planetary Society. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E And wrote the only thing that can get me to cry on queue - Pale Blue Dot.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Chiron0224","CreatedById":147812,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-10T00:18:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222845130\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022151775\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221478735466\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022118251\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022moogoob\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n27 minutes ago, moogoob said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCan\u0027t forget that he was a founding member of the Planetary Society. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E And wrote the only thing that can get me to cry on queue - Pale Blue Dot.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd csicop\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MaxxQ","CreatedById":102622,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-10T01:16:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222845130\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022151775\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221478735466\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022118251\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022moogoob\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, moogoob said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCan\u0027t forget that he was a founding member of the Planetary Society. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E And wrote the only thing that can get me to cry on queue - Pale Blue Dot.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe aforementioned Pale Blue Dot:\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022344\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/wupToqz1e2g?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022459\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCarl Sagan\u0027s Cosmos series is also what introduced me to Vangelis. \u00A0His music is what is being played in the background of this video (he also did the soundtrack for Blade Runner,\u00A0Chariots of Fire, and other films). \u00A0Here\u0027s the entire piece (Heaven and Hell, Pt. I), including the second half featuring vocals from Jon Anderson, former vocalist for Yes. \u00A0I\u0027ve set the link to start at the relevant part, that was used as the theme music for Cosmos (the entire piece is around 22 minutes long):\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022344\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/FLLJA-sm-z8?start=768\u0026amp;feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022459\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cubinator","CreatedById":150330,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-10T02:37:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u0022We began as wanderers and we are wanderers still. We have lingered long enough on the shores of the cosmic ocean. We are ready at last to set sail for the stars.\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Curveball Anders","CreatedById":107529,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-10T11:33:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222845320\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022151775\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221478745436\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150330\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022cubinator\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n8 hours ago, cubinator said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u0022We began as wanderers and we are wanderers still. We have lingered long enough on the shores of the cosmic ocean. We are ready at last to set sail for the stars.\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLater visualised by Erik Wernquist as \u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YH3c1QZzRK4\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EWanderers\u003C/a\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"katateochi","CreatedById":35181,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-10T11:53:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI meant to post this here yesterday, I\u0027d been getting what I\u0027m calling the Sagan bug all day (until \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/61954-majorjim/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002261954\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/61954-majorjim/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Majorjim!\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0told me how to fix it - don\u0027t disable eclipses in scatterer)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022xvnyvD3.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022625\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/xvnyvD3.jpg\u0022 style=\u0022width:600px;height:auto;\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Red Iron Crown","CreatedById":12858,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-10T11:55:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMoved over to the Lounge, KSP Discussion is for KSP stuff. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"monstah","CreatedById":95210,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-11T12:18:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u00A0\u003Cem\u003Eam\u00A0\u003C/em\u003Ewearing that shirt to work today!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}